  "title": "Warehouse Assistant #77377",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Wholesaler – Building Materials</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Warehouse Assistant</strong></li><li>Working Location: Gul Avenue</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Monday-Friday: 8:00AM - 5:00PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to $3500 + Quarterly Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage the distribution of products, maintaining inventory accuracy.</li><li>Utilizing barcode scanners to scan products, packaging finished product (shrink wrapping, boxing, labeling) and staging finished product.</li><li>Operate forklifts, overhead cranes, and other warehouse machinery for loading and moving items.</li><li>Verify and inspect incoming and outgoing shipments for discrepancies.</li><li>Prepare Metal A-frame return shipments.</li><li>Repair/Rebuild Wooden A-frames for LTL shipments.</li><li>Uphold cleanliness and safety standards in the warehouse.</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties which may be assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum O-Levels or relevant qualifications.</li><li>Min 2 years of relevant experience.</li><li>Proficient in computer usage; SAP knowledge is a plus.</li><li>Possess valid forklift license.</li><li>Able to lift up to 35kgs.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#77377 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
